description:
Beat Bobby Flay - Season 5, Episode 2




Who's Your Daddy?

This battle is for the dads when New Jersey's own Chef Gregory Torrech laces up his bootstraps against Moroccan chef Sam Marvin. Restaurateur Scott Conant and Actress and Author Haylie Duff decide who has what it takes to face Bobby in this Father's Day battle. Sophie Flay also appears in this episode to introduce the ingredient for Round 1.




Original Air Date: 11-Jun-2015
